1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
Welcome to my channel.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:15,613
When the orchid is sick and rotten like this,

3
00:00:15,613 --> 00:00:19,930
Don't rush to throw it away,

4
00:00:19,930 --> 00:00:26,657
Let me guide you on how to help it recover quickly.

5
00:00:35,881 --> 00:00:37,881

6
00:00:48,480 --> 00:00:59,422
Remove all rotten leaves so they do not spread to the stem.

7
00:01:24,245 --> 00:01:29,016
The roots are still very healthy.

8
00:01:32,161 --> 00:01:44,080
Use about 1/4 small lemon.

9
00:01:52,170 --> 00:01:57,011
Add 500ml of water.

10
00:02:01,952 --> 00:02:18,940
Soak in this water for about 5 minutes

11
00:02:24,473 --> 00:02:34,503
AFTER 5 MINUTES OF WAIT.

12
00:02:34,503 --> 00:02:44,965
Keep in a cool place to dry.

13
00:02:52,225 --> 00:02:54,225

14
00:02:54,225 --> 00:03:25,673
Use dry paper to absorb water.

15
00:04:25,882 --> 00:04:41,012
Sprinkle some cinnamon powder here to dry and prevent rot.

16
00:04:45,211 --> 00:04:52,010
Keep in a cool place and do not water for 1 week.

17
00:04:57,810 --> 00:05:04,874
AFTER 1 NEXT WEEK

18
00:05:15,443 --> 00:05:43,033
Use about 10g of aloe vera leaves.

19
00:05:43,033 --> 00:05:52,918
Add 500ml of water.

20
00:06:23,114 --> 00:06:30,090
Take a portion into a spray bottle

21
00:06:40,182 --> 00:07:12,182
Watering aloe vera for orchids.

22
00:07:38,547 --> 00:07:48,542
AFTER 3 NEXT WEEKS.

23
00:07:48,542 --> 00:07:57,730
Has sprouted small.

24
00:08:09,714 --> 00:08:38,765
Periodic 7 to 10 days watering and moisturizing 1 time.

25
00:08:44,513 --> 00:09:00,561
AFTER THE NEXT 2 MONTHS.

26
00:09:26,925 --> 00:09:46,918
From now on, fertilize once every 2 weeks and keep the orchid moist to grow stronger.

